<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Appsmith | Open-Source Low-Code Platform</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn about Appsmith's mission to democratize software development through open-source low-code tools.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-container">
        <a href="/" class="logo">Appsmith</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/sign-up">Sign Up</a>
          <a href="/getting-started/setup">Setup</a>
          <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>About Appsmith</h1>
          <p class="hero-description">We're on a mission to democratize software development by making it fast, easy, and accessible for everyone to build custom applications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="content-text">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Appsmith, we believe that every business should have the power to build custom software solutions without the complexity and cost of traditional development. Our open-source low-code platform empowers developers and business users alike to create powerful applications quickly and efficiently.</p>
            <p>Founded with the vision of bridging the gap between business needs and technical implementation, we've built a platform that combines the flexibility of code with the speed of visual development.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="content-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Team collaboration">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Open source">
            </div>
            <h3>Open Source First</h3>
            <p>We believe in transparency and community-driven development. Our open-source approach ensures you're never locked into proprietary solutions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Developer focused">
            </div>
            <h3>Developer-Centric</h3>
            <p>Built by developers, for developers. We prioritize code-level control and flexibility while maintaining the simplicity of visual development.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553484771-371a605b060b?w=64&h=64&fit=crop" alt="Community">
            </div>
            <h3>Community Driven</h3>
            <p>Our vibrant community of developers, contributors, and users shapes our roadmap and drives innovation across the platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Growing Global Impact</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">100K+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Active Developers</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">500K+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Applications Built</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Countries</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">30K+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">GitHub Stars</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">We're a diverse group of engineers, designers, and product experts passionate about making software development accessible to everyone.</p>
        <div class="team-grid">
          <div class="team-member">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=200&h=200&fit=crop" alt="Team member">
            <h4>Abhishek Nayak</h4>
            <p>Co-founder & CEO</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616c2c999ff?w=200&h=200&fit=crop" alt="Team member">
            <h4>Nikhil Nandagopal</h4>
            <p>Co-founder & CTO</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=200&h=200&fit=crop" alt="Team member">
            <h4>Arpit Mohan</h4>
            <p>Co-founder & Head of Engineering</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to start building?</h2>
        <p>Join thousands of developers who are already building amazing applications with Appsmith.</p>
        <a href="https://login.appsmith.com/" class="btn btn-primary">Get started for free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Appsmith. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand: #6366f1;
      --brand-alt: #8b5cf6;
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --surface: #f8fafc;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --muted: #64748b;
      
      --font-heading: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      
      --space-0: 0px;
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-7: 32px;
      --space-8: 40px;
      --space-9: 48px;
      --space-10: 64px;
      --space-11: 80px;
      --space-12: 96px;
      
      --radius-sm: 4px;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    }

    header {
      background: var(--bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      height: var(--space-10);
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-7);
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .mission {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content-text h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .content-text p {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .content-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .values {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .values h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .value-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-8);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface);
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .value-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .value-icon {
      width: var(--space-10);
      height: var(--space-10);
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
    }

    .value-icon img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .stats {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    }

    .stats h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .stat {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: var(--space-2);
    }

    .team {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .team h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .team-intro {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .team-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .team-member {
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-8);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface);
    }

    .team-member img {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .team-member h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .team-member p {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cta {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .cta p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      font-size: var(--space-5);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--brand);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--brand-alt);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--text);
      color: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-8) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        gap: var(--space-4);
      }
      
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      
      .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>